0vehicle%2C%20decoy%2C%20short-range%20air%20defense%2C%20or%20even%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-mothership-coast-guard-drone-aircraft-carrier-south-sea-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emothership%20for%20smaller%20drones.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20severe%20weather%20or%20maritime%20accidents%2C%20it%20assists%20with%20firefighting%2C%20search%20and%20rescue%2C%20and%20emergency%20supply%20transportation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20added%2C%20publishing%20a%20concept%20image%20of%20the%20drone%20spitting%20water%20on%20a%20burning%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20CSBC%2C%20the%20Endeavor%20Manta%20can%20be%20controlled%20using%204G%2C%20satellite%2C%20and%20radio%20signals%2C%20and%20can%20return%20autonomously%20to%20its%20launch%20point%20or%20self-destruct%20if%20it's%20jammed%20or%20hijacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223936%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Endeavor%20Manta%20is%20seen%20traveling%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Taiwan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e37c7069253ccddf9a4bd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Endeavor%20Manta%20reaches%20a%20speed%20of%20up%20to%2035%20knots%2C%20CSBC%20said.%3Cp%3ECSBC%20Corporation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Endeavor%20Manta%20has%20a%20fiber-reinforced%20plastic%20hull%20and%20displaces%20about%20five%20tons%20of%20water%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20relatively%20small%20naval%20craft.%20By%20comparison%2C%20Taiwan's%20Anping-class%20patrol%20boats%20displace%20about%20600%20tons%2C%20while%20its%20Cheng-Kung-class%20light%20frigates%20displace%20around%203%2C200%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECSBC%20said%20its%20new%20drone%20can%20also%20reach%20a%20top%20speed%20of%2035%20knots%2C%20or%20roughly%2040%20miles%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20vessel's%20size%2C%20it's%20highly%20likely%20any%20torpedo%20would%20have%20to%20be%20fitte