w%20with%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BYogi%26quot%3B%20and%20wishes%20for%20everyone's%20happiness.%20Highlighting%20Hindus'%20religious%20tolerance%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20Muslim%20family%20is%20the%20safest%20among%20100%20Hindu%20families.%20They%20will%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20practise%20all%20religious%20customs.%20But%20can%2050%20Hindus%20be%20safe%20among%20100%20Muslim%20families%3F%20No.%20Bangladesh%20is%20an%20example.%20Before%20this%2C%20Pakistan%20was%20an%20example.%20What%20happened%20in%20Afghanistan%3F%20If%20there%20is%20smoke%20or%20someone%20is%20being%20hit%2C%20we%20should%20be%20careful%20before%20we%20get%20hit.%20That%20is%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20the%20state%20has%20witnessed%20no%20communal%20riots%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%202017.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Muslims%20are%20the%20safest.%20If%20Hindus%20are%20safe%2C%20then%20they%20are%20also%20safe.%20If%20there%20were%20riots%20in%20UP%20before%202017%2C%20if%20Hindu%20shops%20were%20burning%2C%20then%20Muslim%20shops%20were%20also%20burning.%20If%20Hindu%20houses%20were%20burning%2C%20then%20Muslim%20houses%20were%20also%20burning.%20And%20after%202017%2C%20the%20riots%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20an%20ordinary%20citizen%2C%20a%20citizen%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20I%20am%20a%20Yogi%20who%20wishes%20for%20everyone's%20happiness.%20I%20believe%20in%20everyone's%20support%20and%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0Mr%20Adityanath%20said%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20is%20the%20most%20ancient%20religion%20in%20the%20world%20and%20stressed%20that%20there%20are%20no%20examples%20in%20world%20history%20of%20Hindu%20rulers%20establishing%20dominion%20over%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanatan%20Dharma%20is%20the%20most%20ancient%20religion%20and%20culture%20in%20the%20world.%20You%20can%20guess%20from%20its%20name.%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20followers%20have%20not%20converted%20others%20to%20their%20faith.%20But%20what%20have%20they%20received%20in%20return%3F%20What%20did%20they%20gain%20in%20exchange%3F%20There%20is%20no%20example%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20where%20Hindu%20rulers%2C%20using%20their%20strength%2C%20have%20established%20dominion%20over%20others.%20Such%20instances%20do%20not%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Namuna'%20Jab%20At%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firebrand%20BJP%20leader%20said%20%26quot%3Bspecimens%26quot%3B%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20benefit%20the%20BJP.%20He%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20nationwide%20march%2C%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Abhiyaan%2C%20was%20actually%20%26quot%3BBharat%20Todo%20Abhiyan%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHe%20criticises%20India%20outside%20India.%20The%20country%20has%20understood%20his%20nature%20and%20intentions.%20It%20is%20important%20for%20the%20BJP%20that%20some%20specimens%20like%20Rahul%20(Gandhi)%20remain%20so%20that%20the%20path%20is%20always%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20wanted%20the%20Ayodhya%20issue%20to%20remain%20a%20controversy.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20the%20Congress%20not%20abolish%20three-talaq%3F%20Why%20did%20the%20Congress%20not%20promote%20Kumbh%20with%20so%20much%20pride%20and%20divinity%3F%20Why%20did%20Congress%20fail%20to%20provide%20world-class%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20country%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BAbiding%20By%20Court%20Ruling%2C%20Otherwise...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20also%20the%20mahant%20of%20the%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%2C%20said%20important%20sites%20of%20Hinduism%20are%20symbols%20of%20India's%20inheritance.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20it%20is%2C%20we%20will%20find%20it.%20We%20will%20show%20the%20world.%20Those%20whom%20God%20has%20given%20eyes%2C%20let%20them%20see.%20What%20happened%20in%20Sambhal%3F%20Sambhal%20is%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Sambhal%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20legal%20battle%20after%20a%20group%20of%20petitioners%20claimed%20the%20Shahi%20Jama%20Masjid%20is%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20an%20ancient%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIslam%20says%20places%20of%20worship%20constructed%20after%20destroying%20Hindu%20temples%20are%20not%20accepted%20by%20God.%20Then%20why%20were%20they%20built%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%20He%20said%20the%20government%20would%20continue%20to%20revive%20temples%20as%20more%20evidence%20is%20found.%20%26quot%3BThe%20scientific%20evidence%20is%20present.%20We%20are%20showing%20where%20they%20are%2C%20and%20we%20will%20address%20them%20one%20by%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Mathura%20mosque%20dispute%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20abiding%20by%20the%20court's%20decision%3B%20otherwise%2C%20who%20knows%20what%20could%20have%20happened%20by%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742967660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frrc61s58_rahul-yogi-split_625x300_26_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyogi-adityanath-if-hindus-are-safe-muslims-are-safe-yogi-adityanath-on-minorities-in-up-8012730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20from%20all%20religions%20are%20safe%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Muslims%20are%20safe%20if%20Hindus%20are%20safe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyogi-adityanath-if-hindus-are-safe-muslims-are-safe-yogi-adityanath-on-minorities-in-up-8012730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22