untries%20like%20Denmark%20and%20Sweden%20%26quot%3Bsensibly%26quot%3B%20limit%20mail-in%20voting%20to%20those%20unable%20to%20vote%20in%20person%20and%20do%20not%20count%20late-arriving%20votes%20regardless%20of%20the%20date%20of%20postmark%2C%20many%20American%20elections%20now%20feature%20mass%20voting%20by%20mail%2C%20with%20many%20officials%20accepting%20ballots%20without%20postmarks%20or%20those%20received%20well%20after%20Election%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-jabs-joe-biden-turned-department-of-justice-into-department-of-injustice-7927957%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20January%20after%20defeating%20Democrat%20nominee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fone-thing-shes-gotta-do-donald-trumps-advice-to-kamala-harris-7997377%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bfree%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20honest%20elections%20unmarred%20by%20fraud%2C%20errors%2C%20or%20suspicion%20are%20fundamental%20to%20maintaining%20our%20constitutional%20Republic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20of%20American%20citizens%20to%20have%20their%20votes%20properly%20counted%20and%20tabulated%2C%20without%20illegal%20dilution%2C%20is%20vital%20to%20determining%20the%20rightful%20winner%20of%20an%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20questioned%20certain%20voting%20methods%20since%20he%20lost%20the%202020%20US%20Presidential%20election%20to%20Democrat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-claims-joe-biden-held-barack-obama-nancy-pelosi-responsible-for-us-2024-election-defeat-7821731%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20polls%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20honest%20and%20worthy%20of%20the%20public%20trust%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Order%20To%20Overhaul%20US%20Elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20citizenship%20proof%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20order%20called%20for%20the%20federal%20voter%20registration%20form%20to%20be%20amended%20so%20that%20prospective%20voters%20must%20provide%20documentary%20proof%20of%20citizenship%2C%20such%20as%20a%20US%20passport%20or%20a%20birth%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20states%20should%20turn%20over%20their%20voter%20lists%20and%20records%20of%20voter%20list%20maintenance%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20for%20review.%20It%20directed%20federal%20agencies%20to%20share%20data%20with%20states%20to%20help%20them%20identify%20noncitizens%20on%20their%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20said%20if%20states%20refuse%20to%20collaborate%20with%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20to%20prosecute%20election%20crimes%2C%20they%20could%20potentially%20lose%20out%20on%20federal%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMail%20ballots%20by%20Election%20Day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20order%20required%20votes%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bcast%20and%20received%26quot%3B%20by%20Election%20Day%20and%20said%20federal%20funding%20should%20be%20conditional%20on%20state%20compliance%20with%20that%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Conference%20of%20State%20Legislatures%2C%2018%20US%20states%20along%20with%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20the%20Virgin%20Islands%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20will%20count%20ballots%20that%20are%20postmarked%20on%20or%20before%20Election%20Day%2C%20regardless%20of%20when%20they%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBallots%20can't%20rely%20on%20QR%20codes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20instructed%20the%20Election%20Assistance%20Commission%20to%20amend%20its%20guidelines%20for%20voting%20systems%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20election%20integrity%26quot%3B.%20That%20would%20include%20guidance%20that%20voting%20systems%20should%20not%20rely%20on%20ballots%20that%20use%20barcodes%20or%20QR%20codes%20in%20the%20vote-counting%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20instructed%20the%20commission%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20appropriate%20action%20to%20review%20and%2C%20if%20appropriate%2C%20re-certify%20voting%20systems%E2%80%9D%20under%20those%20new%20standards%20within%20six%20months%20of%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeigners%20barred%20from%20making%20donations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20order%20also%20barred%20foreign%20nationals%20from%20contributing%20or%20donating%20in%20US%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20nationals%20and%20non-governmental%20organizations%20have%20taken%20advantage%20of%20loopholes%20in%20the%20law's%20interpretation%2C%20spending%20millions%20of%20dollars%20through%20conduit%20contributions%20and%20ballot-initiative-related%20expenditures.%20This%20type%20of%20foreign%20interference%20in%20our%20election%20process%20undermines%20the%20franchise%20and%20the%20right%20of%20American%20citizens%20to%20govern%20their%20Republic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742957340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fn8ja6rs_donald-trump_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trumps-big-move-on-us-elections-to-change-how-america-votes-with-an-india-example-8012041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20right%20of%20American%20citizens%20to%20have%20their%20votes%20properly%20counted%20and%20tabulated%2C%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20illegal%20dilution%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20vital%20to%20determining%20the%20rightful%20winner%20of%20an%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%