%20capital.%20District-level%20parades%20will%20take%20place%20as%20usual.%20Home%20Ministry%20Senior%20Secretary%20Nasimul%20Ghani%20recently%20said%20that%20the%20country%20is%20in%20a%20wartime%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20Yunus%20called%20upon%20the%20countrymen%20to%20resist%20the%20rumour%20through%20awareness%20and%20greater%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20as%20the%20upcoming%20election%2C%20the%20date%20of%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20decided%2C%20would%20come%20near%2C%20the%20rumours%20would%20take%20more%20dangerous%20shape.%20%26quot%3BYou%20all%20know%2C%20who%20are%20behind%20the%20phenomenon%20and%20why%20they%20are%20spearheading%20these%20(rumours)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20asked%20the%20people%20to%20look%20for%20the%20source%20of%20the%20rumour%20whenever%20they%20hear%20any%20such%20misleading%20gossip%20instead%20of%20ignoring%20them%20%26quot%3Bas%20many%20experienced%20war%20experts%20are%20working%20round%20the%20clock%20spending%20unlimited%20money%20behind%20these%20rumours%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bmain%20objective%20to%20thwart%20the%20July%20Uprising%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20overall%20unity%20is%20severely%20irritating%20them.%20They%20want%20to%20break%20the%20unity.%20You%20will%20not%20even%20realise%20their%20innovative%20techniques.%20You%20do%20not%20even%20understand%20when%20you%20became%20a%20pawn%20of%20their%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAlways%20keep%20in%20mind%20we%20are%20in%20a%20war%20situation.%26quot%3B%20The%20interim%20government%20chief%20did%20not%20cite%20any%20specific%20example%20of%20such%20rumours%20but%20several%20of%20his%20advisers%20in%20the%20cabinet%20have%20said%20conspiracies%20were%20underway%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%20particularly%20using%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20destabilise%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%2C%20however%2C%20said%20his%20administration%20sought%20United%20Nations%20cooperation%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20rumours%20and%20disinformation%20and%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%2C%20who%20recently%20visited%20Bangladesh%2C%20%26quot%3Bassured%20us%20of%20extending%20the%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeposed%20premier%20Hasina's%20regime%20was%20ousted%20in%20a%20student-led%20mass%20protest%20spearheaded%20by%20now-defunct%20Students%20against%20Discrimination%20on%20August%205%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%2C%20who%20was%20in%20France%20at%20that%20time%2C%20flew%20home%20and%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Chief%20Adviser%20of%20the%20interim%20government%20three%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%2C%20whose%20experiment%20of%20poor%20men's%20banking%20earned%20him%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%2C%20was%20in%20a%20protracted%20row%20of%20the%20past%20regime%20for%20obscure%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20political%20parties%20and%20analysts%20said%20during%20Yunus'%20past%20seven-month%20rule%20ultraright%20and%20Islamist%20elements%20created%20a%20space%20in%20the%20political%20arena%20and%20they%20were%20spearheading%20a%20campaign%20to%20sideline%20the%20forces%20in%20favour%20of%20the%201971%20Liberation%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20leaders%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%2C%20which%20led%20the%20Liberation%20War%20in%201971%2C%20were%20arrested%20or%20on%20the%20run%20at%20home%20or%20abroad%20to%20evade%20trial%20on%20charges%20like%20mass%20murders%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20in%20Bangladesh's%20domestic%20International%20Crimes%20Tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%2C%20some%20parties%2C%20some%20groups%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20seem%20as%20if%2010971%20never%20happened...%20trying%20to%20erase%20it%20from%20memory%2C%26quot%3B%20Secretary-General%20of%20ex-premier%20Khaleda%20Zia's%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20Mirza%20Faklhrul%20Islam%20Alamgir%20told%20a%20party%20rally%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20once%20collaborated%20in%20the%20(Pakistani%20troops')%20massacre%20-%20those%20very%20people%20-%20are%20now%20speaking%20louder%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20somehow%20smell%2C%20some%20quarters%20are%20trying%20to%20belittle%20the%201971%20(liberation%20War)%26quot%3B%20while%20several%20of%20his%20party%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20in%20near%20identical%20tones%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%2C%20however%2C%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20his%20speech%2C%20recalled%20those%20who%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%20during%20the%20Liberation%20War%2C%20saying%20March%2025%20is%20a%20day%20of%20massacre%20that%20remains%20stigmatised%20in%20the%20history%20of%20human%20civilisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20this%20night%20in%201971%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20occupation%20forces%20brutally%20opened%20fire%20on%20innocent%2C%20unarmed%20and%20sleeping%20Bangalees%20and%20killed%20thousands%20of%20people.%20Since%20March%2025%2C%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20had%20raised%20armed%20resistance.%20Bangladesh%20became%20independent%20through%20a%20nine-month%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742954160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj4vjvr9g_muhammad-yunus-afp_625x300_19_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-plays-down-bangladesh-coup-rumours-festival-of-rumours-8012008%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muhammad%20Yunus%20asked%20the%20people%20to%20look%20for%20the%20source%20of%20the%20rumour%20whenever%20they%20hear%20any%20such%20misleading%20gossip%20instead%