fewer%20than%2010%20warnings%20combined%20from%202015%20to%202021%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what's%20contributing%20to%20the%20rise%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20word%2C%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20acting%20CPSC's%20chairman%2C%20Peter%20Feldman%2C%20told%20PIRG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo-thirds%20of%20the%20products%20that%20received%20warnings%20in%202024%20came%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20the%20PIRG%20report%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20facing%20a%20flood%20of%20Chinese%20consumer%20products%20that%20violate%20US%20safety%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20Feldman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20CPSC%20identifies%20illegal%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20is%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20unreachable%2C%20unfindable%2C%20or%20uncooperative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20a%20warning%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20safety%20officials%20are%20not%20able%20to%20make%20progress%20with%20a%20company%20concerning%20a%20recall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20hazardous%20products%20included%20a%20foldable%20step%20stool%20that%20could%20collapse%20or%20tip%20over%2C%20a%20line%20of%20e-bike%20batteries%20prone%20to%20overheating%20or%20catching%20fire%2C%20infant%20loungers%20that%20posed%20a%20risk%20of%20suffocation%20or%20entrapment%2C%20and%20bike%20helmets%20that%20didn't%20meet%20US%20safety%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20products%20that%20received%20warnings%20were%20sold%20by%20third%20parties%20on%20Amazon's%20and%20Walmart's%20marketplaces.%20In%20at%20least%20one%20instance%20each%2C%20both%20retailers%20agreed%20to%20contact%20customers%20about%20affected%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20all%20products%20offered%20on%20its%20site%20are%20required%20to%20comply%20with%20applicable%20laws%20and%20regulations.%20The%20company%20also%20notifies%20customers%20of%20product%20updates%20through%20a%20dedicated%20page%20in%20page%20in%20their%20Amazon%20accounts%20called%20%26quot%3BYour%20Recalls%20and%20Product%20Safety%20Alerts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PIRG%20analysis%20also%20found%20two%20items%20with%20warnings%20that%20were%20sold%20on%20Shein's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20recalled%20products%2C%20the%20report%20found%20that%20those%20sold%20exclusively%20online%20were%20twice%20as%20likely%20to%20violate%20a%20US%20safety%20standard%20than%20those%20sold%20in%20physical%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20while%20eight%20products%20were%20recalled%20that%20were%20exclusively%20sold%20on%20Temu%2C%20the%20PIRG%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20no%20Temu%20items%20received%20warnings%20last%20year%20because%20all%20companies%20involved%20cooperated%20with%20the%20recall%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ecommerce-brands-record-safety-warnings-us-consumer-watchdog-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742940229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e2ff41b8b41a9673fbaa0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ecommerce-brands-record-safety-warnings-us-consumer-watchdog-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20consumer%20safety%20watchdogs%20say%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20product%20warnings%20boils%20down%20to%20one%20word%3A%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ecommerce-brands-record-safety-warnings-us-consumer-watchdog-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ben%20Affleck%20tried%20to%20make%20acting%20a%209-to-5%20job%20because%20he%20hated%20spending%20time%20away%20from%20his%20kids%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224892%5C