o%20on%20a%20snack%20or%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20decide%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20vending%20machine%20you'd%20like%20to%20have%20(personal%20products%2C%20food%2C%20electronics)%2C%20you'd%20secure%20a%20location%20by%20asking%20busy%20facilities%20to%20either%20rent%20you%20the%20space%20or%20by%20offering%20a%20profit%20share.%20Then%2C%20you%20buy%20the%20vending%20machine.%20It's%20a%20low-lift%20startup%20that%20can%20turn%20a%20good%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f0c9272-c099-4c53-96ca-2ac02adb1dd9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Pet%20care%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20I%20got%20my%20first%20dog%20in%202022%20that%20I%20started%20to%20see%20how%20much%20money%20it%20costs%20to%20have%20a%20pet.%20Not%20only%20do%20you%20have%20to%20shell%20out%20cash%20for%20food%2C%20treats%2C%20and%20toys%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Fbest-pet-insurance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evet%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20always%20seem%20to%20pile%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20American%20Pet%20Products%20Association%2C%20people%20spent%20an%20estimated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famericanpetproducts.org%2Findustry-trends-and-stats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24150.6%20billion%20on%20their%20pets%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20which%20was%20up%20from%20%2490.5%20billion%20in%202018.%20Plus%2C%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20more%20than%2023%20million%20American%20households%2C%20or%20nearly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspcapro.org%2Fresource%2Fnew-aspca-survey-vast-majority-dogs-and-cats-acquired-during-pandemic-still-their-homes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20in%20five%20households%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adopted%20a%20pet%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Society%20for%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20influx%20of%20pet%20owners%2C%20a%20recession%20isn't%20going%20to%20change%20their%20purchasing%20habits%20too%20much%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20essentials%20their%20dogs%20need.%20This%20is%20why%20I'm%20thinking%20of%20pursuing%20a%20side%20hustle%20in%20the%20pet%20industry%2C%20whether%20it's%20starting%20a%20food%20or%20treat%20business%2C%20a%20leash%20and%20collar%20business%2C%20or%20doing%20more%20pet%20sitting%20and%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229651b1cf-acf0-4242-bd39-f27cccba3823%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Tutoring%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20a%20recession%20happens%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20entire%20world%20stops.%20One%20thing%20that%20still%20goes%20on%20is%20school.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20parents%20still%20find%20themselves%20in%20the%20market%20for%20tutoring%20or%20after-school%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20tutor%20of%20varying%20educational%20levels%20for%20your%20child%20at%20various%20price%20points%2C%20it's%20a%20service%20that%20parents%20who%20have%20even%20a%20little%20extra%20disposable%20income%20aren't%20likely%20to%20cut%20if%20it%20means%20their%20child%20can%20get%20ahead%20in%20school%20or%20even%20increase%20their%20scores%20to%20get%20into%20a%20certain%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20done%20tutoring%20before%2C%20but%20after%20looking%20into%20it%2C%20anyone%20can%20set%20up%20a%20profile%20on%20sites%20like%20%3Cspan%3EWyzant%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tutor.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETutor.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20list%20their%20resume%20and%20accomplishments%2C%20determine%20the%20subjects%20they%20want%20to%20tutor%20in%2C%20and%20set%20their%20hourly%20rate.%20From%20there%2C%20parents%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20find%20the%20best%20tutor%20for%20their%20child's%20needs%20and%20their%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20for%20