f%20voter%20rolls%20have%20found%20extremely%20few%20numbers%20of%20noncitizens%20registered%20to%20vote.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fgeorgia-noncitizens-voter-rolls-14532ef49b66f9cbf34ff483d2534280%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeorgia%20found%2020%20noncitizens%20%3C%2Fa%3Eregistered%20to%20vote%20out%20of%20more%20than%208%20million%20registered%20voters%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%2C%2044%20states%20opposed%20a%20Trump%20election%20commission's%20sweeping%20request%20for%20voter%20information%2C%20according%20to%20a%202017%20CNN%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Kansas%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Kris%20Kobach%2C%20vice%20chair%20of%20the%20commission%2C%20had%20said%20the%20data%20would%20eventually%20be%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHasen%20told%20Business%20Insider%20said%20Tuesday's%20EO%20could%20spark%20such%20a%20confrontation%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20see%20what%20happens%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-doge-voter-rolls-executive-order-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742937960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e31d30b8b41a9673fbaf15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-doge-voter-rolls-executive-order-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20wants%20the%20DOGE%20office%20to%20help%20find%20potential%20non-citizens%20on%20voter%20rolls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A645%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-doge-voter-rolls-executive-order-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20Signal%3F%20How%20the%20popular%20encryp