0So%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20do%20know%20is%20that%2C%20as%20far%20as%20we%20know%2C%20the%20claim%20was%20completely%20baseless.%26quot%3B%20Whittaker%20added%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bserious%20report%26quot%3B%20backing%20up%20Musk's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESignal%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20Signal%20Foundation%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20in%202018%20by%20the%20app's%20cofounders%2C%20Rosenfeld%20and%20Brian%20Acton%2C%20who%20also%20cofounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-whatsapp-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20foundation%20has%20five%20board%20members%20and%20serves%20to%20%26quot%3Bsupport%20Signal's%20growth%20and%20ongoing%20operations%20as%20well%20as%20investigate%20the%20future%20of%20private%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignalfoundation.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20guide%20to%20the%20Signal%20app%2C%20including%20why%20it's%20become%20so%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c240555d-54bd-4603-8c62-a51375758972%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Signal%20app%2C%20explained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESignal%20is%20safer%20and%20more%20secure%20than%20most%20messengers%20because%20of%20a%20process%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fend-to-end-encryption%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend-to-end%20encryption%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20This%20works%20by%20encoding%20a%20sender's%20message%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20only%20the%20intended%20receiver%20can%20view%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Signal%2C%20nor%20your%20phone%20company%2C%20nor%20the%20government%20can%20read%20your%20messages.%20That's%20why%20it%20has%20remained%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3C