%20Mr%20Goyal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'THE%20BIG%20TWO'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20topped%20the%20list%20in%20terms%20of%20pace%20of%20growth%2C%20the%20top%20two%20spots%20in%20terms%20of%20size%20of%20economy%20remained%20the%20United%20States%20(%2430.3%20trillion)%20and%20China%20(%2419.5%20trillion).%20Germany%20is%20in%20third%20place%20at%20%244.9%20trillion%2C%20Japan%20in%20fourth%20at%20%244.4%20trillion%2C%20and%20India%20at%20fifth%20at%20%244.3%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20into%20the%20top%20two%20places%20will%20take%20India%20little%20over%20two%20decades%20at%20its%20current%20rate%20of%20growth.%20Though%2C%20it%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20as%20of%20March%2C%202025%2C%20US's%20national%20debt%20stands%20at%20%2436.22%20trillion%2C%20while%20China's%20national%20debt%20as%20of%20September%2C%202024%20stands%20at%20%242.52%20trillion.%20In%20comparison%2C%20India's%20overall%20debt%20as%20of%20September%2C%202024%20stands%20at%20%24712%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIA'S%20GROWTH%20TRAJECTORY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20took%2060%20years%20for%20its%20GDP%20to%20reach%20the%20first%20trillion-dollar%20mark%20(in%202007).%20From%20%241%20trillion%20to%20%242%20trillion%20took%207%20years%20(in%202014)%2C%20Despite%20COVID-19%2C%20India%20reached%20the%20%243%20trillion%20mark%20in%202021.%20The%20journey%20from%20%243%20trillion%20to%20%244%20trillion%20took%20just%204%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20pace%2C%20should%20the%20progression%20continue%20the%20way%20it%20is%2C%20India%20is%20poised%20to%20add%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20to%20its%20GDP%20every%201.5%20years%2C%20and%20could%20likely%20become%20a%20%2410%20trillion%20economy%20by%20end%20of%202032.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Data%20for%20this%20article%20is%20as%20per%20the%20data%20available%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20fo