5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dehydration%20temperature%20is%20adjusted%20based%20on%20the%20consistency%20of%20the%20food.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20chutneys%20are%20dried%20at%20a%20much%20lower%20temperature%20than%2C%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Erajma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20control%20over%20the%20process%20ensures%20that%20each%20dish%20maintains%20the%20same%20texture%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20nutritional%20value%20as%20it%20would%20if%20it%20were%20freshly%20cooked.%20As%20compared%20to%20traditional%20dehydration%20techniques%2C%20which%20can%20extract%20as%20much%20as%2092%20or%2096%20percent%20of%20the%20water%20content%2C%20freeze-drying%20removes%20more%20than%2099%20percent%20of%20the%20water%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20choose%20this%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20spent%20around%20four%20years%20researching%20the%20right%20temperatures%20for%20the%20freeze-drying%20technique%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-3_11zon-1742741055-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2