0customise%20it%20based%20on%20our%20needs.%20We%20gave%20him%20specific%20measurements%2C%20temperature%20settings%2C%20tray%20sizes%2C%20and%20other%20precise%20details%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20connected%20with%20several%20suppliers%20for%20key%20components%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20including%20the%20drying%20chamber%2C%20vacuum%20pump%2C%20heat%20source%2C%20condenser%2C%20and%20trays.%20He%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20connected%20with%20around%20four%20or%20five%20different%20people%20for%20all%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20machine.%20Once%20everything%20came%20together%2C%20we%20had%20a%20freeze-drying%20machine%20built%20specifically%20for%20us%2C%20with%20all%20the%20right%20settings%20to%20preserve%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20homemakers%20become%20financially%20independent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20aspects%20of%20Spice%20Up%20Foods%E2%80%99%20success%20is%20its%20collaboration%20with%20homemakers.%20The%20couple%2C%20along%20with%20their%20co-founder%20Madhu%2C%20wanted%20to%20empower%20homemakers%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20were%20looking%20to%20make%20use%20of%20their%20culinary%20skills%20while%20also%20earning%20an%20income.%20As%20Amit%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20we%20were%20cooking%20from%20our%20kitchen.%20My%20mother%20and%20Shalu%20would%20mostly%20prepare%20the%20meals.%20But%20soon%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20scale%20that%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20bring%20in%20home%20cooks%20and%20help%20them%20turn%20their%20passion%20for%20cooking%20into%20a%20profitable%20business.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20we%20place%20a%20particular%20order%20with%20a%20home%20cook%2C%20we%20thoroughly%20inspect%20the%20ingredients%20and%20vegetables%20before%20sending%20it%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shalu.%20Once%20the%20foo