%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tested%20model%20for%20greywater%20recycling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20Mannat%E2%80%99s%20system%20is%20evident%20in%20her%20own%20home%2C%20where%20the%20prototype%20has%20been%20functioning%20for%20two%20years.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20prototype%20that%E2%80%99s%20developed%2C%203D%20printed%20and%20functional%20with%20all%20the%20connections%2C%20Arduinos%2C%20and%20the%20water%20floats%2C%20which%20is%20working%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20family%20of%20four%2C%20the%20system%20saves%205%2C000%20to%206%2C000%20litres%20of%20potable%20water%20per%20month%2C%20effectively%20recycling%2050%25%20of%20their%20water%20demand.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20investment%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20Rs%202000%2C%20can%20be%20got%20back%20via%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F252861%2Fsubbaraman-m-tamil-nadu-ngo-scope-reuse-save-water-covid-19-handwash-guidelines-who-wastage-greywater-sustainable-hacks-innovation-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaving%20in%20water%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gurneet%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-90-1742799926.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mannat%20with%20her%20prototype.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-90-1742799926.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-90-1742799926-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-90-17427