m%20taking%20part%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20vision%20is%20to%20empower%20households%20to%20take%20control%20of%20their%20water%20usage%20and%20contribute%20to%20a%20more%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMannat%20Kaur%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20an%20inspiring%20example%20of%20how%20youthful%20innovation%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20real-world%20problems%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20impactful%20solutions.%20Her%20greywater%20recycling%20system%20addresses%20water%20scarcity%20and%20promotes%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%2C%20making%20her%20a%20true%20champion%20of%20environmental%20stewardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Megha%20Chowdhury%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Mannat%20Kaur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742806800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D415415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meet%20Mannat%20Kaur%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20who%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20Stockholm%20Junior%20Water%20Prize%20with%20her%20eco-friendly%20greywater%20recycling%20system.%20Her%20innovation%20can%20save%20up%20to%2050%25%20of%20household%20water%20and%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20by%2085%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Therapy%20Programme%20Is%20Giving%20Abuse%20Survivors%20the%20Tools%20to%20Overcome%20Their%20Darkest%20Memories%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20India%20witnessed%20an%208.7%25%20rise%20in%20child%20abuse%20cases%2C%20with%20the%20total%20number%20reaching%20a%20concerning%20162%2C000%20incidents%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB).%20Yet%2C%20for%20many%20survivors%2C%20the%20scars%20of%20childhood%20trauma%20last%20a%20lifetime%2C%20often%20going%20unnoticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnupriya%20Das%20Singh%2C%20senior%20manager%20at%20Arpan%20NGO%2C%20has%20seen%20this%20firsthand.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20child%20deserves%20a%20safe%20environment%20to%20grow%20up%20in.%20We%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20make%20that%20a%20reality%20by%20educating%2C%20empowering%2C%20and%20healing%20the%20lives%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368737%2Fpriyatama-sharma-child-sexual-abuse-survivor-education-women-educate-your-girls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20affected%20by%20sexual%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArpan%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20organisations%20working%20to%20address%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20(CSA)%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20critical%20issue%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20Founded%20in%202007%20by%20Pooja%20Taparia%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20developed%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20prevention%2C%20education%2C%20and%20healing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Taparia%20had%20a%20moment%20that%20changed%20everything.%20%E2%80%9CI%20watched%20the%20play%20named%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E30%20Days%20in%20September%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20understood%20the%20lasting%20trauma%20that%20can%20be%20experienced%20by%20adult%20survivors%20of%20childhood%20sexual%20abuse.%20It%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20do%20something%20through%20my%20organisation%20to%20help.%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20education%20and%20prevention%20to%20stop%20this%20abuse%20from%20happening%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn